{"tid":2459434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[An/iOS] 蓮燈時間靜止器（Web版勿入）","createTime":"2021-03-24T07:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T06:01:56.000Z","uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"edd4abf103f9b93bf184e990d7732ca57d75e1a3","tid":2459434,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">今日教大家點樣<strong>停頓時間</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先望住呢隻金牛<br />\n然後心入面默念<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">「Ratom」</span></strong><br />\n三次<br />\n<br />\n之後撳一撳右上角嗰三粒點<br />\n（唔係最頂嗰粒 係「#1」正右方嗰粒）<br />\n然後撳「以此內容建立新主題」<br />\n你就會發現隻金牛唔再識郁😉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過停頓時間係有後果<br />\n你會發現出咗去呢個po之後<br />\n入任何一個po<br />\n都唔會再load到嘢<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"c\">3.14159265358979323846</code></pre>"},{"pid":"096a48f0509c59bca6c2e6b887594ba118d12756","tid":2459434,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a6f1a538dc0fdce59ecf4ea56c975227e963ec","tid":2459434,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"琴晚咪開過囉"},{"pid":"9ec1f1e88c33a879d1be7b46da4027067e54fcbf","tid":2459434,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a6f1a538dc0fdce59ecf4ea56c975227e963ec","tid":2459434,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"琴晚咪開過囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"冇人睇 想整個A/B testing睇吓係咪個Topic出事<img src=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fi